Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:51.05,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an3}baby I wanna be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.13,0:22:53.91,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\}{\fad(300,300)}{\an3}and trust me…yeah
